# Mapbox GL API Token
# Get a free token at: https://www.mapbox.com/account/tokens/
# 1. Sign up for a free Mapbox account at https://account.mapbox.com/auth/signin/
# 2. Go to https://account.mapbox.com/tokens/
# 3. Create a new token (default token works)
# 4. Copy and paste it below as VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN

VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=your_mapbox_token_here
